Scope-OnExit-Wrap

Running code on scope exit (with pure Perl fallback)



INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Scope::OnExit::Wrap

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Scope-OnExit-Wrap

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/Scope-OnExit-Wrap

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Scope-OnExit-Wrap

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/Scope-OnExit-Wrap/


